      <originalsloc id="aspace_a17c5b45281eeda5ad25d0eb3a509a82">
         <head>Existence and Location of Originals</head>
         <p>The entire collection can be located in the Walter Lippmann Papers (MS 326).   The papers consist of correspondence with an international array of scholars, journalists, heads of state, government officials, and friends. Also included are manuscripts and drafts of his books, columns, and speeches. In addition there are diaries and engagement books, photographs of Walter Lippmann with family and friends, requests to speak or write, honors, and film and audio tapes.</p>
         <p>HM 257 only consists of Series I, Series III, Series V, and Series VII of the main accession, and Series I and Series II of accession 2001-M-077</p>  
